            <pb n="1R"/>
            <p rend="align(right)">
                <placeName>New York</placeName>
                <date>July 9<hi rend="sup">th</hi> 1866</date>
            </p>
            <p>Revd <del>Mr</del>
                <addressee>Isaac Leeser</addressee></p>
            <p rend="Note:"> Revd is written over Mr</p>
            <p rend="indent(4)">
                <placeName>Phila</placeName>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(5)">Dr Sir</p>
            <p rend="indent(6)">I beg to trespass<lb/> on your valuable time so much as to<lb/> ask
                if you would procure a circular<lb/> of the best Catholic Orphan Institution<lb/> in
                your city or vicinity, where a <add>female</add> orphan can<lb/> be thoroughly
                educated &amp; be trained to some<lb/> kind of occupation, so that at the proper
                age<lb/> it will be <sic>independant</sic> of the world &amp; able<lb/> to earn its
                own livehoodâ€”I am induced<lb/> to make this inquiry for a friend living in
                        <placeName>Va<add>?</add></placeName><lb/> who is willing to pay any small
                or reason<hi rend="underline">a</hi><lb/>ble amt towards the proper education of
                this<lb/> child &amp; I will esteem it a great favor if you<lb/> would give me such
                information as I require,<lb/> which from your long acquaintance with the char<hi
                    rend="underline">i</hi><lb/>table institutions of your city, I imagine you
                can<lb/> do readily. Hoping you are in improved health<lb/> &amp; with renewed
                assurances of esteem &amp; an<lb/> apology for thus<add>?</add> intruding on your
                time I am</p>
            <p rend="indent(10)">Yours very Truly</p>
            <p rend="indent(10)"><persName role="author">M. M. Davis</persName>.</p>
            <p rend="indent(8)">
                <placeName>Box 2524 N. Y. P. O.</placeName>
            </p>
            <pb n="1V"/>
            <p rend="align(center)">Notre dame</p>
            <p rend="align(center)">Ready Har<add>?</add></p>
            <p rend="align(center)indent(1)">Mid</p>
            <p rend="align(center)indent(-1)">
                <persName>J. M Sevill</persName>
                <placeName>19 South Na<add>?</add></placeName>
            </p>
